doc.after: Japan Airlines serves 33 international destinations in Asia the Americas Europe and Oceania excluding codeshares The airline s international hubs are Tokyo s Narita International Airport and Haneda Airport Osaka s Kansai International Airport and Osaka International Airport in Itami The airline group also serves 59 domestic destinations within Japan 118
